00:24:07.920 --> 00:24:09.160
y rogarte que diseñes su portada.

00:24:12.590 --> 00:24:13.480
Mira,

00:24:15.640 --> 00:24:16.830
¿no estás cansada?

00:24:27.480 --> 00:24:27.920
Jiang Xiaoyuan,

00:24:28.750 --> 00:24:29.880
